                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Description</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Quantity</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>8000882R91</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Protective Conduit Kit Contains the Following:</para>
                                <para>445171C1, Conduit for Deaeration Hose, 3.5 Inches Long (1)</para>
                                <para>584067C1, Conduit for Heater Return Hose, 10 Inches Long (1)</para>
                                <para>289862C1, Cable Lock Strap (2)</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1</para>
                            </entry>
